  "root_text": {
    "iti33:0.1": "Itivuttaka 33 ",
    "iti33:0.2": "Dukanipāta ",
    "iti33:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti33:0.4": "Dutiyasīlasutta ",
    "iti33:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti33:2.1": "“Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato puggalo yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ sagge. ",
    "iti33:2.2": "Katamehi dvīhi? ",
    "iti33:2.3": "Bhaddakena ca sīlena, bhaddikāya ca diṭṭhiyā. ",
    "iti33:2.4": "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dvīhi dhammehi samannāgato puggalo yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ sagge”ti. ",
    "iti33:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti33:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti33:3.1": "“Bhaddakena ca sīlena, ",
    "iti33:3.2": "bhaddikāya ca diṭṭhiyā; ",
    "iti33:3.3": "Etehi dvīhi dhammehi, ",
    "iti33:3.4": "yo samannāgato naro; ",
    "iti33:3.5": "Kāyassa bhedā sappañño, ",
    "iti33:3.6": "saggaṁ so upapajjatī”ti. ",
    "iti33:4.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti33:4.2": "Chaṭṭhaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti33:0.1": "So It Was Said 33 ",
    "iti33:0.2": "The Book of the Twos ",
    "iti33:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti33:0.4": "Ethics (2nd) ",
    "iti33:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti33:2.1": "“Mendicants, an individual with two qualities is placed in heaven as if delivered there. ",
    "iti33:2.2": "What two? ",
    "iti33:2.3": "Excellent conduct and excellent view. ",
    "iti33:2.4": "A individual with these two qualities is placed in heaven as if delivered there.” ",
    "iti33:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti33:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti33:3.1": "“If a person possesses ",
    "iti33:3.2": "these two qualities—",
    "iti33:3.3": "excellent conduct ",
    "iti33:3.4": "and excellent views—",
    "iti33:3.5": "when their body breaks up, that wise person ",
    "iti33:3.6": "is reborn in heaven.” ",
    "iti33:4.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
